				  - FOSSY_USER,
				    FOSSY_PASSWORD,
				    FOSSY_GROUP_ID,
				    FOSSY_SERVER    : parameters to access fossology server
					                  (defaults: 'fossy', 'fossy', 3, 'http://localhost/repo').
				""")
		)

